{"tid":528890,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"中學雞揀科一定要揀Civil Eng (土木工程)","createTime":"2018-01-14T10:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T13:52:21.000Z","uid":103237,"like":20,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"af41a7d641e1fa7e4e5383916cf2126efdf25224","tid":528890,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:45:02.000Z","msg":"例如Poly仔讀Civil入政府做graduate engineer<br />\n3年後考到牌升普通engineer已經跟master pay scale(mps) point 32-44 暫時起薪已經64k,到你畢業果陣可能已經70k<br />\n已經屌打物理治療果d垃圾醫療科,分分鐘屌打埋你同期d政府醫生律師朋友<br />\n而Civil係最大既engineer公務員體系<br />\n多位過任何其他engine系<br />\n連律政司都係Civil Eng<br />\n<br />\n另外做consultant做政府工程亦有機會做駐地盤工程師,一樣跟政府mps point 32-44<br />\n而且剩跟一單project日日準時天黑前已收工<br />\n<br />\n此外做contractor唔駛考牌<br />\n靠吹水吹雞都可能升到Construction Manager搵8萬10萬一個月<br />\n<br />\n若要生活好<br />\n必定讀Civil"},{"pid":"cab291b79c33f7f40ab8bf234b48163ccc740616","tid":528890,"uid":24696,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:49:05.000Z","msg":"繼續吹"},{"pid":"7260b4bc7e8f41cd3e56f6c2f4268b3e84a639f9","tid":528890,"uid":73241,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大大粒"},{"pid":"64978ad352cf3a1bccb214e479c9bc948184339b","tid":528890,"uid":103237,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>繼續吹</blockquote><br />\n吹咩鬼<br />\n句句事實"},{"pid":"40fc23c8d8b5bbd9bfc2a809f8b074ddba20f593","tid":528890,"uid":132296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:50:54.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"a1445a4edd9a5a3c3d4b01d99a113d38aa6383f7","tid":528890,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T10:52:08.000Z","msg":"吹夠civil未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e924aa15a697b47b52c90ba879d5002aac28109","tid":528890,"uid":35870,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201